results.name: Number of non-isomorphic connected weight-n multiset partitions with no singletons and multiset density -1.
comment: The multiset density of a multiset partition is the sum of the numbers of distinct vertices in each part minus the number of parts minus the number of vertices.
The weight of a multiset partition is the sum of sizes of its parts. Weight is generally not the same as number of vertices.
